[normal]Q29 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Mark Garnier:[bold] T
[normal]he key point of this is, as we heard from you, Mr Larsen,
[normal] right at the beginning,
[normal] that
[normal] this is an immensely complex thing. You do not know whether it is a threshold or a target. There are three knockouts. Nobody is really talking about the knockouts at all. Nobody really understands what the unempl
